text: Cathy Thaxton-Tippett (born March 31, 1957) is an American rower. She competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics and the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1957 births Category:Living people Category:American female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the United States Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Stanford Cardinal rowers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
